The room on the 6th floor was fine and sufficiently roomy (separate beds for the children).	Our room on the fourth floor was clean and overlooked the inside courtyard and so was quiet.	The bed in our room was very comfortable, but it was queen size.	The room was a good size, comfy bed and very clean.	The staff were very friendly and helpful and the room was comfortable, clean and very quiet - i had a room facing the hotel courtyard and it was really peaceful.	The rooms are nice, clean, with cable TV and there is room service.